imdb.title: Ghost in the Shell SAC_2045
imdb.plot: Hired as a mercenary unit, the former members of Japan's elite Section 9 are faced with the sudden appearance of "Post-Human," a being with tremendous intelligence and physical capabilities.

episodes.title: DOMINO EFFECT / Silly Kukushkin
episodes.plot: Members of section 9 seek out a man named Philip Kukushin, a Russian National who seems to know à lot about creation of posthuman.......

episodes.title: CLOSE CALL/I've Awoken
episodes.plot: US special operations forces join the Section 9 team in their fight against a relentless posthuman named Suzuka Mizukane.

episodes.title: FACTOR/1A84
episodes.plot: While extracting information from Kukushkin, the Section 9 team uncovers some shocking information about an AI program developed by the US government.

episodes.title: MEMORIES/Born in Heaven
episodes.plot: Worried Purin might be a spy for the Americans, the Major sends out a crew of Tachikoma to look into her hidden past.

episodes.title: ROOM 101/Man's Search for Meaning
episodes.plot: Togusa finally realizes that he's been trapped in his own memories - and suddenly finds himself in a devastated Tokyo in the year 2045.

episodes.title: N-POWER/How to Build an Independent Nation
episodes.plot: After hearing from Togusa, Batou and the others head to Tokyo; back in Fukuoka, the Major learns that a post-human has hijacked a nuclear submarine.

episodes.title: TRUTH POINT OF CONTACT/Bridge of Promise
episodes.plot: Resurrected as a full-body prosthetic cyborg, Purin tries to hitchhike her way to Tokyo; U.S. special operations forces face Mizukane's wrath.

episodes.title: DEMI DEUS/Those Who Evolve Toward Divinity
episodes.plot: Batou and the group get an update on the post-human situation from Standard; the Major and Purin join the rest of the crew in Tokyo.

episodes.title: LAST RESORT/A Long Slumber
episodes.plot: To take back control of the hijacked nuclear submarine, the Section 9 team targets Mizukane and Takashi Shimamura.

episodes.title: OPERATION STANDOFF/The Battle Begins
episodes.plot: Shimamura wakes up and makes a desperate move, putting Kusanagi and her crew in an impossible position.

episodes.title: DOOMSDAY/The Moon over the Ruined Castle
episodes.plot: Kusanagi and her team do everything they can to stop the United States from implementing its Draconian plan to end the nuclear standoff with "N."

episodes.title: DOUBLE THINK/Event Boundary
episodes.plot: The Section 9 crew members start living their regular lives as if nothing ever happened, and the only one who finds it strange is Kusanagi.

episodes.title: NO NOISE NO LIFE - Sustainable War
episodes.plot: The United States, 2045. Working as mercenaries, the Major and her team, including newbie Stan, defend a gated town from outlaws. Togusa takes a call.

episodes.title: AT YOUR OWN RISK - Divided by a Wall
episodes.plot: Armed by a generous patron, the Raiders attack GHOST with AI Drones. Togusa accepts a new mission from Japan's peace-seeking Prime Minister.

episodes.title: MAVERICK - MIA
episodes.plot: As Togusa dives into cyberspace to track his former team members, the group is detained by a mysterious American organization seeking to employ them.

episodes.title: SACRIFICIAL PAWN - Emissary from the Divide
episodes.plot: While researching the team's disappearance and John Smith, Togusa takes a calculated risk. The GHOST members question the true nature of their mission.

episodes.title: PATRICK HUGE - Gift from God
episodes.plot: Kusanagi and the Ghost team are assaulting the home of one of the richest men in the American empire and end up battled to stay alive, much less fulfil their mission.

episodes.title: DISCLOSURE - Quantized Gospel
episodes.plot: Kusanagi is briefed on the threat to all of mankind when another threat arises, only Kusanagi's and Bato's quick thinking averts a disaster.

episodes.title: PIE IN THE SKY - First Bank Robbery
episodes.plot: Back in Japan after six years, Batou decides to take a break while waiting for his delayed team. Then some amateur bank robbers interrupt the fun.

episodes.title: ASSEMBLE - What Came About as a Result of Togusa's Death
episodes.plot: The Major and Smith clash over Section 9's new mission hunting post-humans. She orders Togusa to investigate a suspected spy near the Prime Minister.

episodes.title: IDENTITY THEFT - The Lonely Struggle
episodes.plot: Section 9 tracks down a post human in Japan, but will they be able to stop it from murdering the prime minister.

episodes.title: Net People - Reasons Leading to Flameout
episodes.plot: Someone is acting as judge, jury, and executioner. Can this be the work of the post-humans? Only Section 9 can get to the bottom of this mystery.

episodes.title: Edgelord: The Revolution of The 14-Year-Olds
episodes.plot: Pudding helps analyze the Thinkpol program while the Major and Togusa search for clues about the post-human middle school student Takashi Shimamura

episodes.title: NOSTALGIA - All Will Become N
episodes.plot: Togusa has a strange episode while analyzing the data confiscated from Shimamaru. When he wakes up, he and Batou out to investigate.
